<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a10Oct1925"><font color="red">10 October 1925</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver): There is a rumour here that Mr Walsh was arrested, that Mr Pound bailed him out and that Mr Walsh is in bad health &hellip; I have no notion where the MS of <b><font face="wake">C</font></b> is at present. I should like this settled before I enter the waste land. Which things being so, I began <font face="wake">D</font>d (otherwise the last watch of Shaun) a few days ago &hellip; </div>
